<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>THE MASTER'S CALL</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngaiun, Lalpa'n hangsan leh thudik;
 Buh lakhawm di'n a sam;
 Buh a min tai, lak ding phat ngakin,
 Nasemte a tawm ui.

[V2]
 Lalpa minin kuonun gunchuh leh,
 Hehpih leh zaidam in;
 Hukdamna manbei thu kipahum,
 Khawvel ah phuongzak un.

[V3]
 2. Chieh unla, mangthaite hukdawk un,
 Gitloh, thim nuoi apat;
 Panpih un hukdam hung hiding in,
 Thempa hatkwl tan un.

[V4]
 3. Gimtheite lawp takin va hilh un,
 Hinna an um dingin;
 Amah, kumsawt Hinna changthak chun,
 Amau na lawp ina.

[V5]
 4. Chieh un, sem un, nitum ding ei tai,
 Khawvel bei pai ina;
 Phat haksa chuh hung tung pai ina,
 Na sem thei ta puoi tiu.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>296</hymn_number>
</song>